ves/category/recensioni/" >Opera</a> </span> <span class="meta-author" title="Author"> <i class="icon-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/massimiliano-maurizi/" title="View all posts by Massimiliano Maurizi" rel="author">Massimiliano Maurizi</a></span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/accademia-di-santa-cecilia-di-roma/" rel="tag">Accademia di Santa Cecilia di Roma</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/akademie-fur-alte-musik/" rel="tag">Akademie für Alte Musik</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/burcu-uyar/" rel="tag">Burcu Uyar</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/daniel-schmutzhard/" rel="tag">Daniel Schmutzhard</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/die-zauberflote/" rel="tag">Die Zauberflote</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/kurt-azesesberger/" rel="tag">Kurt Azesesberger</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marcos-fink/" rel="tag">Marcos Fink</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/miah-persson/" rel="tag">Miah Persson</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rene-jacobs/" rel="tag">René Jacobs</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sunhae-im/" rel="tag">Sunhae Im</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/topi-lehtipuu/" rel="tag">Topi Lehtipuu</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/wolfgang-amadeus-mozart/" rel="tag">Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Accademia di Santa Cecilia di Roma, Akademie für Alte Musik, Burcu Uyar, Daniel Schmutzhard, Die Zauberflote, Kurt Azesesberger, Marcos Fink, Miah Persson, Opera lirica, René Jacobs, Sunhae Im, Topi Lehtipuu, Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" s